{"tid":908892,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"竹野內豐承認分手了！　小17歲女友切心斷5年情…原因曝光","createTime":"2018-11-20T02:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T03:50:55.000Z","uid":1121,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc13919ccac652d006a4b57fde959831de1f5db","tid":908892,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3707/d3707005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3707%2Fd3707005.jpg&h=fd8c08ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲竹野內豐、倉科加奈承認分手。（圖／翻攝自日網、女性自身推特）<br />\n<br />\n記者陳芊秀／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本男神竹野內豐分手了！他和小17歲女友倉科加奈5年前爆熱戀，每年年底必傳婚訊，不過都不了了之，沒想到2018年底卻爆出分手，雙方經紀公司爽快承認「好幾個月前就已經聽說分了。」<br />\n<br />\n據日媒《女性自身》報導，竹野內豐2014年10月戀情曝光，被拍到和倉科加奈的過夜情，隨後公開認愛「我和倉科小姐關係很好。」隨後多次傳出分手消息，兩人戀情仍不受影響，春天時還被拍到疑似半同居。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，竹野內豐和倉科加奈是在7月底分手，且是由女方提出。由於女友一直希望30歲這年結婚，且生日正好是12月23日，幾乎每年都被媒體敲碗「聖誕婚」，雖然他也朝著這個目標進行，最後還是分手，當時他曾被拍到一個人買小菜，回到和媽媽一起居住的家，身形看來有些寂寞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3707/d3707006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3707%2Fd3707006.jpg&h=73030f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲倉科加奈生日12月23日，心願是30歲這年，聖誕節前夕結婚。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3707/e3707007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3707%2Fe3707007.jpg&h=0652d42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲竹野內豐分手後，曾被目擊一個人買小菜回家。（圖／翻攝自日網、女性自身推特）<br />\n<br />\n現年47歲的竹野內豐剛獲選為「2018年日本男性最想成為的臉孔」，近年力求轉型，除了破例開始接演男配角，和綾瀨遙合作日劇《繼母與我的藍調》收視、口碑創下好評。他近年在受訪時，曾分享心中理想的男女關係，「結婚固然很重要，但不是最終的目的地，比起結婚這個形式，我覺得更重要的是雙方互相成長的關係。」"},{"pid":"bc1039cc394fba256e48b27810b3f0db7dd787f7","tid":908892,"uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.hoopchina.com.cn/user/062/4092062/1276060484a7198.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuser%2F062%2F4092062%2F1276060484a7198.gif&h=bb65d105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.hoopchina.com.cn/user/062/4092062/12760604652db61.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fuser%2F062%2F4092062%2F12760604652db61.gif&h=95048768&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"626c5102265617bd1a43fea0f4aefb2f90554666","tid":908892,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UCML3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUCML3.gif&h=fe3b3d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40bdd067624d0e746989afbfb4b4a7d283628ba5","tid":908892,"uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/ZOn3ZBiaVYzFNZYwbqSta1sfBnia9Pog3gr9shBv8081sy7cb9T3FgXCPS92ziblyN4aicppXAIfibFZq9IewIOrAbw/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FZOn3ZBiaVYzFNZYwbqSta1sfBnia9Pog3gr9shBv8081sy7cb9T3FgXCPS92ziblyN4aicppXAIfibFZq9IewIOrAbw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif&h=d24a31a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84d066b77bb6a7358d27613f394d1eeede4be354","tid":908892,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"3d4bd52915d1ce998ee38b261a74b73a02409f46","tid":908892,"uid":34071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1exATRQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1exATRQ.gif&h=593e74a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa61b881bbf5b5821476aafc1e7636f82a2eb265","tid":908892,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a16182ba7e7cd84696f0b4523bcce9d6adb972","tid":908892,"uid":2638,"like":0,